Test your Red Hot Chili Peppers' trivia knowledge with the RHCP Quiz App!  

Click 'Start' to begin the game.  

You will be asked 5 different multiple choice questions with 4 possible answers to choose from.  If you get the question right, you get 1 point out of 5.  

The game will give you the answer after each question is answered.  

When you are done, the game will give you back your results and evaluate how much of a RHCP fan you are!  

Click 'Restart Quiz' to try again!

Enjoy!